<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../421/1041421.xml#xpointer(//*[./st=%22Target+aperture+sights%22])">
Vernier sight</link></part>
</percept>
</representation>
</component>
</visual_percept>
</concept>
</idea>
</sight>
.  It’s marked up to twelve-hundred yards.  This one shoots a mite further.</it>
</indent>

</p>
